f
[a,b]
\displaystyle \int_a^b h_{\epsilon}(x)dx
\epsilon \to 0
\displaystyle \ell= \inf\limits_{\epsilon>0} \int_a^b h_{\epsilon}(x)dx
\displaystyle \left| \int_a^b h_{\epsilon}(x)dx-\int_a^bg_{\epsilon}(x)dx \right| \leq \epsilon(b-a)
s \leq f
\displaystyle \int_a^b s(x)dx \leq \int_a^b h_{\epsilon}(x)dx
\displaystyle \int_a^b s(x)dx \leq \ell
\displaystyle \ell= \int_a^b f(x)dx
